title: Psychedelic Chillout Dub Sampler
description:
A sampler introducing psychedelic ambient chillout dub music, or psydub. Consists of several artists as listed below. This is an introductory collection, with one or two songs of each artist/band. If you like them, feel free to support them, as most  are underground quality music. Enjoy.

Includes:

Siesta Submarina - It's Allright Little Elephant
Kukan Dub Lagan - Spirit Of The Wind
Don Peyote - Phoenix Rising
D Batistatos - Tall Stories
D Batistatos - Shining
Jupiter 8000 - Rubber Dub
Carbon Based Lifeforms - Photosynthesis
Carbon Based Lifeforms - Proton Electron
Vibrasphere - Forest Fuel
Vakuum Sounds - A Journey After A Snake Bite
Siesta Submarina - Arktik Dub
Bluetech - Prayers For Rain (Ott Remix)
Tau Kita - Flying In The Rain
The Sushi Club - Shiosai
The Kumba Mela Experiment - Interstellar Hiss (Sky Is On Fire Dub)
Umberloid (Ott) - Exit Chapel Perilous
Ott - Signals From Bob
Shpongle - Around The World In A Tea Daze
